metadata.name: The Struggling Artist - Teaser/Placeholder
metadata.description:
This token is a temporary placeholder teaser for the upcoming collection The Struggling Artist, to be dropped soon on SuperRare.

The Struggling Artist is a photographic series created by Hugo Faz and Erick Monterrosa as their visual interpretation of the struggles they went through as artistic creators. This collection will feature associated Deca Etches minted by the artist containing the struggles of several invited NFT creators and builders.

This token was minted in advance in order to reserve the right to optionally charge royalties for secondary sales of this collection on OpenSea while not being required to block any other competing marketplaces. This token's metadata may be updated in the future to represent an actual artwork of the collection.
